<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>armchair general • armchair pilot</xh5><p> <i>armchair general—</i>smb. who speaks critically of military matters, etc. but has no real experience: You’ve never served in the military, which confirms my suspicion that you’re just another <u>armchair general</u>.</p><p><i>armchair pilot—</i>a person whose hobby is computer based flight simulation: Authentically modeled after the F-16 control column, this controller is intended for the advanced <u>armchair pilot</u>.</p> </entry>
